10:11.220 --> 10:20.231
somebody needed to make a phone call home in that 
building. I think there were two or three public

10:20.551 --> 10:27.139
telephones in the lobby of the Y. And to my 
knowledge, they were the only phones on the campus

10:27.159 --> 10:32.205
that the students could use to call home. And when 
your dad arrived, the building had already been

10:32.860 --> 10:38.888
built, and the Y was a going organization. Do you 
remember about the number of staff that he had as a

10:40.110 --> 10:45.438
part of the Y? Well,

10:46.239 --> 10:55.371
Jay Gordon Gay was the assistant secretary.

10:56.393 --> 11:01.500
