only two people that worked on the live program.

11:03.688 --> 11:17.360
The other people that worked in the building, of 
course, they had the secretary and custodians,

11:03.688 --> 11:17.360
but the barbers were, I mean, they were, that was a 
private barber. I mean, it was a public barber

11:17.380 --> 11:18.982
shop. And the confectionery was owned by Mr. 
Sparks and Mr. Casey. And so, as far as the staff was

11:26.128 --> 11:30.812
concerned, it was just, my dad and Jake Warren 
Gates. Describe your dad physically and then

11:33.565 --> 11:47.019
describe his personality and what he believed in, 
