Well, first of all, he was a Presbyterian elder. In 
fact, in those days, it was before the the sessions

12:01.876 --> 12:31.495
that rotated so he was an elder and he was as long as i 
remember he was an elder on the session of the

12:01.876 --> 12:31.495
president one of the things he was concerned about 
as a as a secretary of the ymca was the fact that uh

12:01.876 --> 12:31.495
well in those days the students would come to a m in 
september There were no cars, no automobiles. If

12:34.772 --> 12:42.042
they went anywhere, they hitchhiked or they went 
on the train or the bus, but primarily they

12:34.772 --> 12:42.042
