13:00.832 --> 13:26.558
carousing, and of course there weren't any women 
around, but he was concerned about the kinds of

13:27.128 --> 13:30.553
things that they had to do on the weekends. And one 
of the things that the YMCA did was they sponsored a

13:30.673 --> 13:38.524
free show, a free movie. In fact, the only movies in 
