13:38.544 --> 13:48.978
assembly hall and it was run by the YMCA. They had 
movies on Tuesday night and Saturday night for the

13:48.998 --> 13:55.347
general public. the students and anybody else 
that wanted to go. On Wednesdays and Fridays, they

14:01.420 --> 14:10.028
had what they called,

