let me see if I can remember the name. Anyway, they 
were there to benefit. The clubs could sponsor a

14:13.031 --> 14:19.537
movie and whatever they could make from it. And on 
Sunday, the YMCA had a a movie, they showed a movie

14:23.575 --> 14:31.081
starting at one o'clock on Sunday and it was free 
and everybody wanted to go. Would those Sunday

14:31.101 --> 14:39.228
movies be more serious religion related or would 
they just be the cheapest thing? Some of them

14:39.328 --> 14:43.992
