was not part of the rules enforcement staff. Not 
that I know of. Okay. So his was to be a positive

15:16.218 --> 15:20.982
factor. I guess, you know, He did an awful lot of 
counseling, I'm sure, and I don't know what his

15:25.152 --> 15:42.390
title might have been, or what level of, you know, 
he might have been considered as.

